0.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=209.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Nuclear vs. solar</span><hr size=1> I would be happy to take this elsewhere, point out a thread? Anyway...<br>
<br>
Yales's early post mentioned &quot;solar out to Saturn&quot; before this debate got started, and since Nasa is becoming pretty settled on the technology to be used on JIMO, comparing solar to nuclear on a similar scale vehicle for the &quot;next&quot; hypothetical mission to Saturn seemed to make sense.<br>
